      "navSections": [
        {
          "title": "Inspiration",
          "layout": "grid-1",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "Personality frameworks like MBTI have become a shared social language for people to introduce themselves and connect with others, especially among young users. They are widely used to initiate conversations, express identity, and navigate social interactions. Conversations often begin with labels like “I’m an ENFP” or “I’m an INFJ.”"
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "mediaName": "SocialScene.png"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "However, these interactions often remain shallow. People struggle to move beyond labels and express who they really are."
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "This project — Living Jade — explores how personality representation can move beyond static categories to support more meaningful social interaction."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Problem",
          "layout": "grid-2",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "While widely adopted, personality systems rely on fixed categories often fail to reflect how people actually experience and express themselves.Through research and user studies, several key issues were identified:"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "· Personality is reduced to static labels"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "· Test results lack stability over time"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "· Systems fail to support meaningful, ongoing interaction"
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "mediaName": "Persona1.png"
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "mediaName": "Persona2.png"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "<strong style='color:#9dd3ff; font-size:22px; font-weight:700;'>How might we represent personality as a dynamic and evolving system that supports deeper self-expression and more meaningful social interaction?</strong>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Design Development",
          "layout": "grid-1",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "We began by rethinking how personality could be represented beyond static categories. Early explorations focused on shifting from discrete personality types to continuous and multi-dimensional representations.We experimented with different ways of structuring personality traits, comparing categorical labels with vector-based models that allow gradual variation and evolution over time."
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "mediaName": "Development.png"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "To make abstract personality data more interpretable and expressive, we explored visual metaphors for representation. Jade was chosen as a cultural and symbolic medium due to its associations with balance, variation, and layered meaning. We experimented with how different personality traits could be translated into visual properties such as color, texture, and form."
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "mediaName": "Development2.png"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "We explored different interaction models to move beyond one-time personality testing toward continuous engagement. Early concepts included static test-based outputs versus interactive systems that allow users to explore and refine their personality over time. Through iteration, we focused on integrating AI-driven dialogue to support ongoing interpretation and self-reflection."
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "mediaName": "Development3.png"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "As the system evolved, we integrated representation, interaction, and interpretation into a unified framework. The final design combines dynamic personality vectors, AI-based interpretation, and jade visualization to create a continuous and interpretable experience. We iteratively refined the system to balance expressiveness, interpretability, and usability."
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "mediaName": "Development4.png"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": ""
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "mediaName": "14-景观步道.png"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "System & Interaction",
          "layout": "grid-1",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "The system enables users to explore personality through continuous interaction:"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "· Users input preferences through questions and interactions"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "· A dynamic personality vector is generated and updated over time"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "· AI provides contextual interpretation and explanation"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "· Personality is expressed through evolving jade representations"
            },
            {
              "type": "image",
              "mediaName": "14-景观步道.png"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Challenges & Reflection",
          "layout": "grid-1",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "One of the main challenges was balancing abstraction and interpretability. While dynamic representations allow flexibility, users still need clear explanations to understand their personality."
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "Another challenge was translating a computational model into an intuitive and meaningful interface."
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "html": "This project highlights the importance of designing AI systems that are not only technically robust, but also interpretable and human-centered."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
